	(135, 'footer4', '<p><a target="blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/exaquemm" data-mce-href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/exaquemm"><span><i class="fab fa-linkedin-in fa-sosial-media link_hover"></i></span></a> <a target="blank" href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXXDuhPvK3JlgJ4kiIIFvLQ" data-mce-href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXXDuhPvK3JlgJ4kiIIFvLQ"><span><i class="fab fa-youtube fa-sosial-media link_hover"></i></span></a><br></p>', ''),
	(136, 'home_label1', '<p><span style="font-size: 18pt;" data-mce-style="font-size: 18pt;">Apakah Anda perlu <span style="color: rgb(169, 2, 0);" data-mce-style="color: #a90200;"><strong>menyederhanakan</strong></span>&nbsp;sistem antrean Anda, <span style="color: rgb(169, 2, 0);" data-mce-style="color: #a90200;"><strong>merampingkan</strong></span> perjalanan pelanggan Anda, atau <span style="color: rgb(169, 2, 0);" data-mce-style="color: #a90200;"><strong>meningkatkan</strong></span> pengalaman pelanggan Anda?</span></p>', ''),
	(137, 'home_label2', '<p>&nbsp;<img src="https://www.exaque.com/public/content/1902180415398260.png" data-mce-src="https://www.exaque.com/public/content/1902180415398260.png"> </p>', ''),
	(138, 'home_label3', '<p><span style="font-size: 18pt;" data-mce-style="font-size: 18pt;">Lebih dari 30 tahun Qmatic mengembangkan berbagai <span style="color: rgb(169, 2, 0);" data-mce-style="color: #a90200;"><strong>solusi cerdas</strong></span> untuk membantu Anda melakukan&nbsp;tiga hal itu.</span></p>', ''),
	(139, 'home_label4', 'Add Text Here..!', ''),
	(140, 'home_label_video', 'Click here for a glimpse into our world', ''),
	(141, 'delivery_title', 'Memberikan Layanan yang Efisien', ''),
	(142, 'delivery_label', 'Solusi Exaque dapat meminimalkan waktu tunggu yang sebenarnya dan waktu tunggu yang dirasakan, menargetkan promosi dan mencari staf dengan keahlian yang sesuai kebutuhan pelanggan, serta mempersonalisasikan setiap titik sentuh.', ''),
	(143, 'solition_intro', '<p style="text-align: center;" data-mce-style="text-align: center;"><span>Semua solusi&nbsp;Exaque dirancang khusus dan direkayasa agar&nbsp;dapat diintegrasikan dan memiliki kinerja yang optimal. Solusi Exaque&nbsp;memiliki desain yang moderen,&nbsp;pengoperasian yang andal, perangkat keras dan perangkat lunak yang berkualitas,&nbsp;dan&nbsp;dukungan garansi selama 2 tahun. Klien-klien Exaque yang&nbsp; memaknai solusi Exaque sebagai instalasi yang rendah risiko, pemasangan yang cepat dan pemutakhiran&nbsp;sistem secara berkala. Hal ini mengurangi kompleksitas solusi dan total biaya kepemilikan, menjaga perjalanan pelanggan Anda bekerja secara andal setiap hari dan dimanapun Anda ingin melakukan bisnis.</span></p>', ''),
	(144, 'solition_label', 'SOLUSI-SOLUSI EXAQUE', ''),
	(145, 'solutions_label', '<p><span>All Qmatic solutions are purpose designed and engineered for tight integration and optimal performance. From R&amp;D through warranty support, we take full responsibility for the design, operability, and quality of our hardware and software solutions. For our clients, that intense focus on the total quality of our customer journey management solutions translates to low risk installation, accelerated deployment, and upgrades as you need them. It reduces the complexity of your solutions and the total cost of ownership, keeping your customer journey working reliably and as you need it to every day and everywhere you do business.</span></p>', ''),
	(146, 'roadmap_title', 'The roadmap for a successful customer journey and the resources to see it through.', ''),
	(147, 'solutions_content', '<p>Qmatic supplies market-leading business solutions for single and multi-location organizations. Across the globe, we help companies make sure their customers and employees enjoy efficient and enjoyable interactions. Spanning every engagement point from online appointment booking capabilities to post-service insights, our solutions can clarify and construct the best possible interactions.</p><p>Every piece of the Qmatic solution is integrated and pervasive across your organization. You can give your customers the ability to connect with you however it suits them best, and engage the exact right employee for any interaction, whether they are on site or connecting virtually.</p>', ''),
	(148, 'qmatic_solutions_label', 'QMATIC SOLUTIONS', ''),
	(149, 'qmatic_links_label', 'Add Text Here..!', ''),
	(150, 'delivery_healthcare_title', 'Memberikan Layanan yang Efisien', ''),
	(151, 'delivery_healthcare_label', 'Add Text Here..!', ''),
	(152, 'patient_label', 'Download a Patient Experience Insight Guide', ''),
	(153, 'patient_content', '<span>Download one of our guides, focused on the key consideration’s healthcare providers need to consider when digitizing the patient journey</span>', ''),
	(154, 'improving_label', 'Exaque Membantu Meningkatkan Pengalaman Pasien', ''),
	(155, 'blog_title', 'Baca Artikel Blog Kami', ''),
	(156, 'solo_red_label', 'Ciptakan Perjalanan Pelanggan yang Lebih Baik dengan Solo.', ''),
	(157, 'koisks_red_label', 'Add Text Here..!', ''),
	(158, 'delivery_retail_title', 'Memberikan Layanan yang Efisien', ''),
	(159, 'delivery_retail_label', 'Exaque membantu merek bisnis Anda menjadi alat bantu yang tepat dalam memahami, mengantisipasi, dan memenuhi berbagai harapan dengan perjalanan pelanggan Anda dengan mulus dan lancar, mulai dari daring dan ponsel sampai pengalaman di dalam toko.', ''),
	(160, 'delivery_public_title', 'Memberikan Layanan yang Efisien', ''),
	(161, 'delivery_public_label', 'Add Text Here..!', ''),
	(162, 'patient_public_label', 'Download a Government Efficiency Insight Guide', ''),
	(163, 'patient_public_content', 'Download one of our guides focused on the challenges public sector organisations face in delivering efficient services in our ‘under pressure’ series.', ''),
	(164, 'improving_public_label', 'Exaque Membantu Meningkatkan Efisiensi Pemerintah', ''),
	(165, 'public_blog_title', 'Baca Artikel Blog Kami', ''),
	(166, 'orchestra_widget_content_info', '<h1>Mencakup berbagai kebutuhan Anda</h1><p><span>Di bawah ini Anda memiliki pilihan terhadap modul-modul yang dapat membantu mewujudkan perjalanan pelanggan yang sempurna.</span></p>', ''),
	(167, 'solition_content', '<ul class="list--arrow-bullets list--columns list--larger"><li><a href="sistem-manajemen-antrian" data-mce-href="sistem-manajemen-antrian">Sistem Manajemen Antrian</a></li><li><a href="pemesanan-jadwal-janji-temu" data-mce-href="pemesanan-jadwal-janji-temu">Pemesanan Jadwal Janji-Temu (<i>Appointment</i>)</a></li></ul>', ''),
	(168, 'journey_label', '<h5>Mengintegrasikan dan meningkatkan setiap titik interaksi mulai dari pra-kedatangan sampai pasca-pelayanan.</h5>', ''),
	(169, 'journey_sub_label', '<p><span><em>Customer Journey Management</em>&nbsp;(CJM) atau Manajemen Perjalanan Pelanggan dari Exaque menciptakan pelanggan dan karyawan menjadi lebih bahagia. Hal ini dimulai pada saat pelanggan terhubung melalui interaksi Internet (daring), ponsel dan interaksi fisik sampai mendapatkan umpan balik. Dengan memahami perjalanan pelanggan Anda akan memperoleh perspektif yang lebih luas tentang bagaimana pelangan terhubung dan mendapatkan&nbsp;informasi&nbsp;serta sumber daya yang Anda butuhkan untuk meraih kesuksesan.</span></p>', ''),
	(170, 'heading1_label', 'Kami adalah perusahaan yang menyediakan solusi teknologi sistem antrean untuk menghubungkan orang dengan layanan.', ''),
	(171, 'content1_label', '<p>Kami percaya bahwa&nbsp;sekarang ini&nbsp;pengalaman pelanggan adalah perjalanan&nbsp;yang menyeluruh&nbsp;dan berkesinambungan yang di awali dari ponsel&nbsp;sampai pertemuan&nbsp;fisik. Exaque hadir untuk memberikan solusi teknologi dan wawasan membuat perjalanan semulus dan senyaman mungkin bagi pelanggan, pasien, warga masyarakat, dan juga staf yang memberikan pelayanan.</p>', ''),
	(172, 'content2_label', '<p>Kami bekerja keras untuk menyediakan solusi dan wawasan manajemen perjalanan pelanggan yang menyenangkan pelanggan, membantu para staf, memperkuat merek, dan meningkatkan pengalaman.<br>Singkatnya, <strong>kami ingin menciptakan perjalanan pelanggan yang lebih baik.</strong></p>', ''),
	(173, 'heading2_label', 'Nilai-Nilai Inti', ''),
	(174, 'heading3_label', 'Add Text Here..!', ''),
	(175, 'content3_label', 'Add Text Here..!', ''),
	(176, 'career_article1', '<p>There’s nothing more fulfilling than being part of a team of smart, experienced people who share a set of core values and a common end goal. That’s what makes Qmatic so special. For more than three decades, our people have worked together to create better customer journeys.</p><p>Our mix of innovation, culture, and spirit has made Qmatic the global leader in customer journey management technology solutions. Our experienced teams have strong commitment, work well together and take ownership for promises and deliveries. Clients across the world rely on Qmatic for our unique approach. We look at the whole lifecycle of the customer journey. Then we engage precise expertise and knowledge in development, manufacturing, sales, installation, maintenance, and support to tailor the right solution for each client.</p><p>We are proud of our international working environment. We have created an atmosphere that values the skills of our individuals and the relationships with our clients. Together we will keep building the success of our company for many years to come.</p><p>It’s important that our employees believe in the business and are committed to shared success. In return, we offer a unique chance to work with a fast-growing company where individuals truly can make a difference.</p>', ''),
	(177, 'welcome', 'Welcome to the Qmatic family', ''),
	(178, 'welcome_article', '<p>Our working culture is the foundation of our company. It is at the heart of how we act internally, how we think, feel, act and behave, and how we deliver great customer experiences. We are more than a group of people working to produce attractive products and solutions. We are a genuine, inclusive team working in a dynamic environment.</p><p>Together we deliver on every promise we make. With consistency and caring, we build trust in all relationships. In the end it is the people who make the difference.</p>', ''),
	(179, 'quote1', '<em>"I would say that what makes Qmatic most special is the atmosphere and the spirit. The athmosphere between departments and functions is very open."</em>', ''),
	(180, 'quote2', '<em>"I like the size of the company. I have the possibility to influence and what I do makes a difference. Qmatic is a great place for me to use my skills as well as develop new ones."</em>', ''),
	(181, 'qmatic_why', 'Why Qmatic', ''),
	(182, 'qmatic_description', '<p>We stand behind your success.</p><p>Qmatic employees have the unique chance to work with a fast-growing international company in a creative, entrepreneurial environment. In our flat organizational structure, you get the chance to work “where it happens” – close to the product and the business. You can own your professional development and advance your career as you work across global boundaries to develop ideas that shape the future of our business, products and decisions.</p>', ''),
	(183, 'benefit_title', 'Qmatic benefits include:', ''),
	(184, 'benefit_list', '<ul><li>Competitive salary and benefits</li><li>Training and support to get you started on the right foot</li><li>Global employee survey</li><li>Knowledge sharing resources and platforms</li><li>Regular sales and product training</li><li>Yearly appraisals</li></ul>', ''),
	(185, 'go_with_us', 'Go with Us', ''),
	(186, 'go_with_us_info', '<p>Working with us means you have the ability to perform both strategic and operational tasks, and enjoy working with people from different cultures. You know how to build long-term relationships and recognize the value of a customer-focused approach.</p><p>If this sounds like you, take a look at our ongoing and recent opportunity listings.</p>', ''),
	(187, 'contact_gmap', '<p><br data-mce-bogus="1"></p>', ''),
	(188, 'home_industry_title', 'Pilih industri Anda:', ''),
	(189, 'solution_title', 'Jelajahi Solusi dan Produk Kami', ''),
	(190, 'product_article', '<p><span>Produk-produk perangkat lunak&nbsp;dan perangkat keras Exaque memiliki&nbsp;fleksibilitas dan bisa diintegrasikan ke dalam sebuah solusi yang lengkap.&nbsp;Exaque juga menyediakan dukungan garansi untuk setiap komponen dalam ekosistem pengelolaan perjalanan pelanggan.</span></p><p><span>Bagi klien kami, satu sumber untuk pembelian, penerapan dan dukungan berarti lebih sedikit kompleksitas dan risiko, implementasi dan peningkatan yang lebih cepat, dan total biaya kepemilikan yang lebih rendah. Anda dapat mempercayai bahwa produk dan solusi sistem antrean Exaque&nbsp;akan bekerja dengan andal dan sesuai kebutuhan perjalanan pelanggan Anda setiap hari dan di mana pun Anda berbisnis.</span></p>', ''),
	(191, 'discovery_label', '<h5><br></h5><h5><span>Membuat sebuah perjalanan pelanggan yang benar-benar berdampak dapat diawali dengan membangun sebuah pengetahuan yang jelas dan bermanfaat terhadap bagaimana pelanggan berinteraksi dengan lingkungan tempat pelayanan Anda, tim Anda serta penawaran-penawaran yang Anda berikan. Program <em>Customer Journey Discovery</em>&nbsp;Qmatic secara sistematis menjelaskan setiap bagian dari pengalaman pelanggan&nbsp;agar dapat terus berkembang.</span></h5>', ''),
	(192, 'library_paper_title', 'Laporan Resmi', ''),
	(193, 'library_video_title', 'YouTube', ''),
	(194, 'home_text_1', 'Minimalkan Interaksi dan Jaga Jarak', ''),
	(195, 'home_text_2', '<p>Dengan solusi antrian ponsel, pengunjung dapat melakukan antre tanpa menyentuh layar sentuh kios, serta pengunjung dapat menunggu di mana pun sambil menjaga jarak dengan pengunjung lain.</p>', ''),
	(196, 'home_text_3', 'Optimalkan Pelayanan Pelanggan Anda', ''),
	(197, 'home_text_4', '<h5>Kami menyediakan teknologi kinerja tinggi dan solusi manajemen antrean yang efektif untuk membantu pelayanan pelanggan Anda sebaik mungkin.</h5>', ''),
	(198, 'ap_grid_title', 'Manfaat utama dari sistem pemesanan janji-temu daring:', ''),
	(199, 'title', 'Manajemen Antrian vs. Manajemen Perjalanan Pelanggan', ''),
	(200, 'headline', '<p>Kesalahan umum&nbsp;yang banyak membingungkan antara Manajemen Antrian dengan Manajemen Perjalanan Pelanggan.</p>', ''),
	(201, 'title12', 'Smart digital solutions to safeguard customers and employees', ''),
	(202, 'headline12', 'Add Text Here..!', ''),
	(203, 'apptext_3', 'Contoh Penerapan', ''),
	(204, 'widgetHomeTitle', 'Mitigasi COVID-19', '');
